--- !u!114 &5835037943940191135
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 4632570268071773123}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 7c74432ea036acc428c5688b3a06ac49, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  _dialogues:
  - _phrases:
    - "<b>VW - Beetle</b>\n\nAhh\u2026 this reminds me of those classic movies\nwith
      \u201CHerbie\". This was real classy stuff! \r\n\r\nI\u2019m pretty sure this
      is the\noldest car in here.\r\n"
  - _phrases:
    - "<b>BMW - E34</b>\n\nThe legendary true classic of the late 80s.\r\nA road
      warrior!\r\n\r\nStrong, boxy, and impossible \nto park in small spaces.\r\n"
  - _phrases:
    - "<b>Opel - Manta</b>\n\r\nFamous for its sporty look, bold colors, \nand a
      reputation louder than its engine.\n\r\nA car with more personality than most
      drivers could handle.\n\r\nEither way, it turned heads\u2026 even today.\r\n\nA
      true icon of the 70s!\n"
  - _phrases:
    - "<b>Audi - Quattro</b>\n\nWhat a wonderful car! I still remember \nwhen it
      was released back in 1980.\r\n\r\nWow... more than 45 years ago.\r\n\n"
  - _phrases:
    - "<b>Mercedes-Benz - SL300</b>\n\nAh yes, the timeless classic of the 50s!\r\n\nElegant
      curves, iconic doors, \nand pure vintage charm.\r\n"
  - _phrases:
    - The chest is <b>locked</b>!
  - _phrases:
    - Sounds like an opening chest.
  - _phrases:
    - Sounds like an opening chest.
